short.ar: قم بإنشاء مستندات Google وSheets وSlides وForms على الفور من شريط المتصفح الخاص بك بسهولة بنقرة واحدة.

short.ta: உங்கள் உலாவி பட்டியிலிருந்து ஒரு கிளிக்கில் Google Docs, Sheets, Slides, அல்லது Forms உடனடியாக உருவாக்கவும்.
short.te: మీ బ్రౌజర్ బార్ నుండి ఒక క్లిక్ సౌలభ్యంతో తక్షణంగా గూగుల్ డాక్స్, షీట్స్, స్లయిడ్స్ లేదా ఫార్మ్స్ సృష్టించండి.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Quickly create Google Docs, Sheets, Slides, or Forms directly from your browser bar. No more navigating through multiple screens—get instant access to your Google Drive workspace and start new projects with just one click.

Why Install?

Instant Access: Create new Google Docs, Sheets, Slides, or Forms without leaving your current tab.

Time-Saver: Streamline your workflow by jumping straight into document creation.
Versatile: Ideal for students, professionals, and anyone who needs quick access to Google Drive tools.

User-Friendly: Simple and intuitive, with minimal setup required.

Boost your productivity today with "Google Docs Create Quickly" and enjoy seamless access to your digital workspace!
